There different types of the grant types in the oAuth2.0

Out of them AUthorization code and the client credentials are the mostly used 

In Authorizaton code type authorization mechanism the authorization code is needed and those are passed. for example
if the user needs some redirection then in this case these are used. and this is more used

In client credential authorization mechanism the authorization code is not need and rest are same
if we need to request own data and no redirection happend then in this case those are used.



